  - Creation=Man's Primordial Birthright
By: Jâmi
---
Man, in regard to his corporeal nature, stands at the lowest point of
degradation; nevertheless, in regard to his spiritual nature, he is at
the summit of nobility. He takes the impress of everything to which he
directs his attention, and assumes the colour of everything to which
he approaches.
